OL,4,CStudent loan rates absurd, say MPs
OL,5, The inflation measure used to set
OL,6, interest rates on student loans is
OL,7, "absurd", says a report from MPs.
OL,9,FThe government uses RPI - the Retail
OL,10,FPrices Index - which the Treasury
OL,11,FSelect Committee says is "flawed" and
OL,12,Fshould be "abandoned".
OL,14,FThe rise in that measure will push
OL,15,Finterest rates on student loans for
OL,16,Ftuition fees up to 6.3% in the autumn.
OL,18,FThe Department for Education defended
OL,19,Fthe continuing use of RPI, saying it
OL,20,Fprovided "consistency over time".
